WEBVTT

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:03.216
When I asked one altruist
why donating her kidney made sense to her,

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:05.960
she said, "Because it's not about me."

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:08.776
Another said,

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:11.056
"I'm not different. I'm not unique.

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:14.416
Your study here is going to find out
that I'm just the same as you."

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:18.536
I think the best description
for this amazing lack of self-centeredness

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.416
is humility,

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:23.536
which is that quality
that in the words of St. Augustine

00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:25.080
makes men as angels.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.816
And why is that?

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:30.616
It's because if there's
no center of your circle,